  Kong2--khi2-lai5 long2 si7 mia7--lah. A-eng sit8-chai7 tin-sioh kap in Sin-thiam e5 jit8-chi2, bo5-nai7 ho2-keng2 put-siong5. Ji7-chap8 goa7 ni5 cheng5, Sin-thiam ngou2-choan pit-giap8, Jit8-seng ka3 i oh8 cho3 seng-li2, choan chau2 goa7-khau2. M7-si7 tiam3-a2-thau5 pang3 hoe3, to7-si7 pan7-toh chhoan5 hoe3, sang3 hoe3. Nng7-lang5 cha2-am3 cho3-hoe2, Sin-thiam kan-na7 e7-hiau2 tiau5-tit8-a2 kong2: ¡§A-eng, in kong2 lan2 khan-chhiu2, goa2 to7 ai3 che7 kim-kau-i2 neh.¡¨ Goan5-lai5 nng7-lang5 peN5-che7-hoe3, chit8-e5 ni5-thau5, chit8-e5 ni5-boe2 seN. A-eng chiok-chiok cha2 chap8-ko3-goeh8, pun--lai5 e5 si5 nng7-lang5 hou7-siong kio3 mia5 kio3 koan3-si3, tu5-liau2 chhu3-piN keh-piah kap chin-tong5-a2, ia7 bo5 lang5 chai. M7-chai si7 Sin-thiam khah ban7 chhut-si3, A-eng hiam5 i gin2-a2-seng3, bo5-tek bo5-tiaN7, cho3 seng-li2 ma7 khah chiN2--tam7-poh8-a2. ¡§Ai3 thoa--a7,¡¨ Jit8-seng kio3 A-eng tioh8 ka7 ka3: ¡§Bo5 boa5 boe7 giam2-nge7--lah.¡¨ Sui5 nng7-lang5 kam2-cheng5 chin3-tian2, Jit8-seng lai7-lai7 goa7-goa7 e5 seng-li2 tauh8-tauh8-a2 pang3 hou7 in. ¡§Chit-e5 chha5-thau5-ang-a2,¡¨ sui-jian5 A-eng chin chai Jit8-seng beh ka7 siu cho3 sin-pu7, m7-koh, A-thiam gong7-gong7 boe7-hiau2 piau2-tat8 ai3-i3. Bo5 chhui3 bo5 sui2, hou7 A-eng to e7 khi3, kaN2 u7-iaN2 ka-ti7 bo5 tit-lang5-ian5? Boe7 tit-lang5-ai3?
  A-eng si7 koe3-lu7--liau2, jit8-jit8 cho3-hoe2, A-thiam cho3-tioh8 khang-khoe3 koh tioh8 put-si5 hou7 A-eng hoah tang hoah sai, kan-na7 khoaN3 A-eng hiah me2-chheN2, A-thiam keng3 to7 khah che7 koe3 ai3--louh. Koh ti7 lak8-chap8 ni5-tai7, chng-kha gin2-a2 po2-siu2, khah ham-ban7 piau2-tat8 kam2-cheng5. Na7 mai3 ou-kau2 Tan5 put-si5 teh o-lo2, A-eng m7-chai ka-ti7 joa7 tit-lang5-ian5. Na7 mai3 ou-kau2 Tan5 tiN5-cheng5 toe3-au7, A-thiam boe7 chhia-to2 chhou3-thang2 siap chin-cheng5! ¡§Chit-khoan2 e5 ki-kut, cho3¡y¼Ò¯S¨à¡zsiong7-ho2.¡¨ Ou-kau2 Tan5 siong7-gau5 kong2 ho2-thiaN-oe7. U7-iaN2 A-eng san2-thiu, pheng7 in bu2--a ke chiok koan5-toa7, sui-jian5 e7-hoai5 chiam-chiam, chhui3-phoe2 pi2 in bu2--a iau2 khah phong3-phoe5--leh. Kang7-khoan2 chhui3-a2 se3-se3, m7-koh bo5 teng5-thah8-khi2. Siong7-seng5 iau2-si7 bak8-sin5 oah8. ¡§Bak8-boe2 e7 kong2-oe7--ou5!¡¨ Lian5 Jit8-seng to o-lo2 ou-kau2 Tan5 chit8-e7-chhiu2 to7 liah8 chhut A-eng siong7-be5-lang5 e5 sou2-chai7. Chha to7 chha Sin-thiam na2 e2-kau2, ia7 boe7-hiau2 oh8. ChhiuN7 A-eng cho3 thau5-mng5, ¡§kin-a2-jit8 hoe na2 teh thou3-sin-lui2--ou5,¡¨ ou-kau2 e7 nai nng7-ku3: ¡§Ke joa7 kiau joa7 sui2--leh!¡¨ Ah na7 phiN7-tioh8 hoe-hun2-bi7, ¡§Oa5! Phang-kong3-kong3,¡¨ hoah kah toa7-se3-siaN: ¡§Kin-a2-jit8 pa2 koh chui3--a, bian2 chiah8--louh.¡¨ Sin-thiam chhai7 ti7 piN--a, chhou3-thang2 tit8-tit8-gia5, khi3 koh bo5-te3 thau2, kian-kian-a2 piN3 bo5-lian2.
  A-eng ji7-chap8-ji7-hoe3 hit-ni5 tang-boe2, ou-kau2 Tan5 in che2-hu li7-iong7 cho3-ni5-boe2-hi3 chhiaN2 kheh-hou7. Sin-thiam kong2 bo5-ai3 khi3, ¡§Li2 m7-khi3 tong5-giap8 e7 an2-choaN2 kong2? Bo5 kap lang5 kau-poe5 beh nah cho3 u7 seng-li2?¡¨ Jit8-seng kong2-tioh8 Sin-thiam e5 sim-koaN-khut-a2: ¡§Toa7-han3 tioh8 chhoa7--a, lan2 chit-pan7--e5, kap lang5 pi2-pheng7 kaN2 e7 su--lang5!¡¨ Ki5-sit8 Sin-thiam kok-hong-bin7 long2 boe7 su--lang5, cheng-chha bo5 ou-kau2 hit-ki-chhui3 nia5. I chin chai in lau7-pe7 teh ka7 chaN2-khui3, m7-koh, to7-si7 bo5 hoat-tou7 chhiuN7 ou-kau2 Tan5 an2-ne siaN2-mih oe7 to thih8, koh kong2 kah hou7 A-eng e7 chhui3-chhio3 bak8-chhio3. Kap A-eng na2 chah8 chit8-teng5 bou5-a2, hou7 Sin-thiam chiaN5 khou2-nau2. M7-chai ai3 an2-choaN2 tut8-phoa3, lai5 khap8-tioh8 A-eng e5 sim, tit tioh8 i e5 i3-ai3.
  Kui-boe2, Sin-thiam sai2 suh-pah-luh, chai3 Jit8-seng kap A-eng khi3 hou7 ou-kau2 Tan5 in che2-hu chhiaN2. Toh khui chap8 goa7 te3. Jit8-seng sui5 hou7 lang5 chhiaN2-jip8 toa7-thiaN, A-eng ma7 hou7 A-mui5 khiu2-khi3 cha-bou2-toh. ¡§Tang-si5 beh kiat-hun?¡¨ A-eng chhio3--leh chhio3--leh bo5 in3--i. ¡§A-eng, goa2 thai3 thiaN-kong2 li2 bo5-ai3 ke3--i-leh,¡¨ A-mui5 oat8-thau5 khoaN3 Sin-thiam: ¡§Bai2-bai2-a2-be2 ma7 u7 chit8-pou7-chhu2, kou2-i3 to7 ho2--lah.¡¨ A-eng khin-siaN kong2: ¡§Kan-na7 chit8-ki-chhui3 kam5 chit8-e5 chih8, long2 bo5 goa7-ian5, cho3 m7-chiaN5 seng-li2 ne.¡¨ ¡§KaN2 si7 beh tai7-li2 Ui5-tha-lou7 e5 keng-giau-koan5--a?¡¨ A-mui5 chin him-sian7: ¡§Kheh-hou7 phah-phah--leh, pang3 hou7 lin2 A-thiam i to7 cho3 boe7 li7--louh.¡¨ ¡§Iau2 teh kau-siap8--leh, m7-chai theh8 e7 tioh8--bo5?¡¨ Teh kong2 e5 si5, A-eng khoaN3 ou-kau2 Tan5 oa2 khi3 Sin-thiam hit-te3 toh keng3-chiu2. Kui-toh lim-tang lim-sai, thiaN boe7 chheng-chho2. Ti7 chit-khoan2 e5 tiuN5-bin7 i u7 khah tan-sim Sin-thiam, chai-iaN2 chhui3 tang7 boe7 iaN5--lang5, e7 hou7 lang5 koan3-chiu2. Ou-kau2 Tan5 chang2-tioh8 ki-hoe7 it-teng7 e7 ka7 sah-se2, siu-li2--chit8-e7. Bak8-chiu thau-lioh--leh, u7-iaN2 chai kui2-lo7 poe. I koh boe7 lim, pau chham2--e5. Bo5 joa7 ku2, ou-kau2 Tan5 chit8-chhiu2 chiu2-kan, chit8-chhiu2 ni poe-a2 kiaN5 oa2--lai5. ¡§Goa2 keng3 tak8-e5...¡¨ ¡§Boe7-sai2--tit,¡¨ A-mui5 sui5 na5-chah8: ¡§Tioh8 sui5-e5-a2 lai5.¡¨ ¡§An2-ne goa2 keng3 A-eng,¡¨ ou-kau2 Tan5 chit8-e7 chhiu2 kui-poe bih-luh to3 loh8 au5: ¡§A-eng li2 sui5-i3 to7 ho2.¡¨ ¡§Goa2--leh?¡¨ A-mui5 chiu2-poe phang5--leh: ¡§Li2 kan goa2 sui5-i3--lah.¡¨ ¡§KhoaN-khoaN-a2 si7, A-mui5-a.¡¨ Ou-kau2 Tan5 chhoe7 phang7 seh loh8-lai5 che7: ¡§Tu2-chiah ti7 hia kap in piaN3 kui2-lo7 poe, ma7 tioh8 hou7 goa2 chiah8 chhai3--leh.¡¨ Ou-kau2 Tan5 chhai3 na2 ngeh, chhui3 na2 oe7: ¡§M7-si7 teh pun5-ke-kui, A-thiam bian2 saN-poe to7 ka7 khoan2--khi2-lai5-a.¡¨ Kong2-tioh8 chiaN5 chhau3-iang7: ¡§A-thiam beh kap goa2 piaN3--oh? Cha--leh! Tan2 koe3