  Sio2-khoa2 thau2 chit8-e7 khui3, jim2 boe7 tiau5 A-eng koh khi3 in hit-e5 chha5-thau5-ang-a2, Sin-thiam thai3 boe7-hiau2 tng lang5 bin7-cheng5 kong2 chit-khoan2 oe7--leh? Ah bo5, nng7-lang5 cho3-hoe2 kong2 se3-siaN-oe7 ma7 ho2. KhoaN3 tui3 Sin-thiam hit-te3 toh, bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 i ti7 hia. Mng7--lang5, ¡§khi3 liah8-thou3-a2--lah!¡¨ Chit8-si3-ke3 chhoe7-chhoe7--leh, long2 bo5 khoaN3-kiN3 iaN2. Tang-si5-a2 cha2 kiu ti7 suh-pah-luh hoe3-tai5 lai7 teh khun3. Sui-jian5 hoah-kun5 hoah lim chiaN5 lau7-jiat8, ke-a2-bin7 teng-hoe2 ma7 kng-iaN3-iaN3, A-eng soah u7 bo5-khim5 bo5-khip8 e5 khang-hi-kam2. Bak8-chiu cheng5 e5 Sin-thiam, tiau5-tit8 koh kou2-i3, boe7 oe7-soaN oe7-chui2. Aih, to7-si7 boe7-hiau2 khui-chhui3--lah.
  ¡§A-thiam--a, A-eng--a.¡¨ Hiong5-hiong5 thiaN-tioh8 lang5 teh kio3, A-eng si7 kin2 chau2 oa2. ¡§A-thiam--leh? Lin2 a-pa na2-chhiuN7 phoa3-peN7 e5 khoan2--ou5...¡¨ ThiaN-tioh8 an2-ne, A-eng chong5 jip8 toa7-thiaN. KhoaN3 Jit8-seng toa7-liap8-koaN7 se3-liap8-koaN7, bin7-sek liam5-mi chheN, liam5-mi peh8, chiok kan-khou2 e5 khoan2. ¡§Kin2 chai3 lai5 khoaN3 i-seng!¡¨ Sui5 u7 cha-pou-lang5 tau3 moh chiuN7 chhia-teng2. A-eng bo5 khoa3 kio3 A-thiam, chhia sai2--leh, to7 long7 kau3 peN7-iN7 koa3 kip-chin2. A-thiam chheN2 si7 chheN2--lai5, iau2-si7 A-eng khah giam2-nge7. Chong5-cheng5 chong5-au7, kip-chin2-sek i-seng cheng3-thau5 khoaN3 che7--a: ¡§Ka-chai3 cha2 sang3--lai5, sim-chong7 hoeh-iu5 that tiau5--leh, tioh8 kin2 phah thong....¡¨ Chit8-e7 thiaN boe7 thoat gui5-hiam2, tioh8 toa3 ka-hou7-peN7-pang5 koan-chhat8. A-eng m7-kaN2 li7-khui, kio3 Sin-thiam tng2-khi3 kong2 hou7 a-i chai, i beh tiam3 peN7-iN7. ¡§Ma7 ho2,¡¨ A-thiam goa7-saN thng3 hou7 A-eng thah8: ¡§Goa2 tng2--khi3 sui5 lai5.¡¨
  Ka-hou7-peN7-pang5 jit8-kong-teng chio3 kah na2 jit8-si5-thau5--leh, chhng5-thau5 tau3 ke-si, chhng5-teng2 tih toa7-tang5. A-eng tui3 khau2--a tham3 kui2-lo7 pian3. Kau3 e7-poaN3-me5, sit8-chai7 thai3 thiam2--leh, che7--leh soah khun3--khi3. Han7-bin5-si5-a2 han7-bin5-si5, tut8-jian5-kan chheN2--lai5. ¡§A-pa--lah?¡¨ ¡§Khun3 kah chin loh8-bin5, goa2 chhoa7 li2 lai5 chhia-te2 khun3.¡¨ ¡§Ah u7 iau3-kin2--bo5?¡¨ ¡§U7 in teh kou3, bo5 iau3-kin2--lah.¡¨ A-eng boe7 ki3-tit an2-choaN2 khi3 chhia-te2 khun3--e5. Kui-me5 chhia lai5 chhia khi3, khoaN3-tioh8 Jit8-seng it-tit8 lau5-chhin3-koaN7, bin7-sek chheN-sun2-sun2, hat heng-kham2-a2 thiaN3... Chhiak chit8-e7 chheN2--khi2-lai5, jit8-thau5 i2-keng chhut--lai5-a: ¡§Goa2 thai3 thiaN a-pa kui-me5 haiN-haiN-kio3....¡¨ Peh khi2 kha-thoa A-thiam to7 beh long7 khi3 peN7-pang5, chiah hoat-kak bo5 chheng7 goa7-saN....
  Siu3-tin i2-keng iang Jit8-seng e5 oaN7-thiap-toa7 Tan5 Eng5-chin3 chai3 lai5 ti7 peN7-iN7. Jit8-seng na2-chhiuN7 chin hi e5 khoan2, lian5 beh peng2-sin to bo5 khui3-lat8, kong2-tioh8 oe7 phaN3-siaN phaN3-siaN. Siu3-tin kam2-sim A-eng: ¡§Ka-chai3 kin2 chhia--lai5, hu3 kiu3--tioh8, bo5 to7 gui5-hiam2--louh.¡¨ ¡§Hit-chun7 a-pa bin7-sek chheN-sun2-sun2, kan-khou2 kah haiN-haiN-kio3, koaN7 it-tit8 piaN3, oah8 beh kiaN--lang5...¡¨ A-eng ka7 Siu3-tin lam2--leh, chin-cheng5 lau5-lou7: ¡§A-pa na7 khi3..., ah, a-i--a, goan2 kam-goan7 chiat-hoe3-siu7 hou7 a-pa sio-thiN--lah!¡¨ ¡§A-mih-tou7-hut, li2 e5 hau3-sim, i u7 hok-khi3 chiah8 pah-hoe3--a-lah.¡¨ Khia7 ti7 piN--a e5 Sin-thiam tiam7-chut-chut, chin kam2-tong7 e5 khoan2.
